OL,3,CPlans revealed for Haut du Mont
OL,4,Cmemorial
OL,6,FMore detail can be seen in a fly-
OL,7,Fthrough video of the proposed site at
OL,8,FPier Road.
OL,10,FPlans have been revealed for a
OL,11,Fmemorial and garden, to remember the
OL,12,F10 people who died in the explosion at
OL,13,FHaut du Mont in December 2022.
OL,15,FThe site will primarily be transformed
OL,16,Finto a garden, including an area where
OL,17,Fthe names of those who died will be
OL,18,Fwritten on seating and there will be
OL,19,Fquiet spots where people can sit and
OL,20,Flook across St Aubin's Bay.
