OL,6,FThere will be also be a separate play
OL,7,Farea for young children and the
OL,8,Ffavourite flowers of those died, among
OL,9,Fother suggestions from their families
OL,10,Fand former residents.
OL,12,FKarlene McGinness' mother, Kathy, died
OL,13,Ffollowing the explosion. She is among
OL,14,Fthe family members whose suggestions
OL,15,Fhave been incorporated.
