OL,3,CPlans revealed for Haut du Mont
OL,4,Cmemorial
OL,6,FKarlene says: "Our mum's home always
OL,7,Fhad an incredibly welcoming and warm
OL,8,Ffeel, which was reflective of the
OL,9,Floving, happy, and caring person that
OL,10,Fshe was. So it's important to us that
OL,11,Fthe memorial site has personal
OL,12,Felements which can reflect the kind of
OL,13,Fperson that she was.
OL,15,F"We hope that once it's in place,
OL,16,Fit'll be a pleasant space where we can
OL,17,Fgo to reflect, remember our mum and
OL,18,Freminisce with our family and her
OL,19,Ffriends about all the good times.
