OL,6,F"Our mum loved nothing more than
OL,7,Fplaying with her grandchildren. It
OL,8,Fwill certainly be a place we'll go
OL,9,Fwith our children to play, talk about
OL,10,Fall our lovely memories of her, and
OL,11,Fkeep her memory alive."
OL,13,FJersey Government's Principle
OL,14,FArchitect, Barry Freeman, added: "This
OL,15,Fhas been one of the most heartfelt and
OL,16,Fimportant things I have worked on in
OL,17,Fmy 33-year career.
