OL,6,F"We've focused our attention, of
OL,7,Fcourse, on the families and the
OL,8,Fdisplaced. We've spent a lot of time
OL,9,Fwith them - specifically over the last
OL,10,Fyear - and going through their
OL,11,Ffeelings, aspirations and reflections
OL,12,Fon what they'd like to see".
OL,14,FThe designs will now be submitted for
